Key improvements in yt-study (7):
1. Adaptive depth analysis (SHORT / MEDIUM / LONG) by video duration.
2. 2-pass topic segmentation with timestamped parts for 30min+ videos.
3. Quiz scaling by duration (9-15 questions).
4. SRT subtitle extraction for improved reliability (instead of json3 parsing).
5. Obsidian and Notion output integration.
6. Multi-language output configuration.
7. Optional Deep Research follow-up workflow.
